descp2: string, list or None, default 'default-target' Specify the column name in the data to use as target. If 'default-target', the standard target column a stored on the server is used. If ``None``, all columns are returned as data and the target is ``None``. If list (of strings), all columns with these names are returned as multi-target (Note: not all scikit-learn classifiers can handle all types of multi-output combinations)
